  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69fe86322f2d4be0f9e35b88",
      "text": "任天堂法務部",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778288188,
      "updated": 1778288188
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff09730000000000331ace",
      "text": "[任天堂]の[法務部]のこと",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778321779,
      "updated": 1778321796
    },
    {
      "id": "69febc750000000000db003a",
      "text": "✂ [任天堂法務部が最強と言われがち]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778302070,
      "updated": 1778302130
    },
    {
      "id": "69fea9ad000000000073a818",
      "text": "✂ [任天堂法務部は別に最強ではない]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778297262,
      "updated": 1778302123
    },
    {
      "id": "69febcc30000000000db003d",
      "text": "✂ [最強法務の戦場違い]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778302148,
      "updated": 1778302154
    },
    {
      "id": "69febc630000000000db0039",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778302052,
      "updated": 1778302052
    },
    {
      "id": "69fead2f000000000073a825",
      "text": "これ多角的視点として纏めると良記事になりそうな匂いがする[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778298160,
      "updated": 1778302052
    },
    {
      "id": "69feae8e000000000073a82d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778298511,
      "updated": 1778298511
    },
    {
      "id": "69fefd6700000000001de81b",
      "text": " [カービィ]の名前の由来は、[ドンキーコング]訴訟問題で[ユニバーサル]と戦った弁護士の名前からきているって本当なんだろうか[HelloPeople.icon]",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1778318695,
      "updated": 1778318758
    },
    {
      "id": "69fefd8c00000000001de81d",
      "text": " \tたまにネットで見かける。",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1778318733,
      "updated": 1778318737
    },
    {
      "id": "69fefdb600000000003c440e",
      "text": " \t任天堂の裁判事案であって、法務部の出来事ではないか。",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1778318775,
      "updated": 1778318803
    },
